er Up\"\n|-\n| rowspan=4|1992 || ''Rachel's Dream'' || Man in Dream || Television short\n|-\n| ''[[Agatha Christie's Poirot|Poirot]]'' || Frank Carter || Episode: \"One, Two, Buckle My Shoe\"\n|-\n| ''Friday on my Mind'' || Sean Maddox || 3 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Business with Friends]]'' || Angel Morris || Television film\n|-\n| 1993\u20131994 || ''[[Cracker (UK TV series)|Cracker]]'' || DCI David Bilborough || 10 episodes\n|-\n| 1995 || ''[[Hearts and Minds (TV Drama 1995)|Hearts and Minds]]'' || Drew Mackenzie || 4 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1996 || ''[[Our Friends in the North]]'' || Nicky Hutchinson || 9 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Hillsborough (1996 film)|Hillsborough]]'' || Trevor Hicks || Television film\n|-\n| 1999 || ''Killing Time \u2013 The Millennium Poem'' || Millennium Man ||\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2000 || ''Wilderness Men'' || [[Alexander Von Humboldt]] || 3 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Clocking Off]]'' || Jim Calvert || 2 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2001 || ''[[Othello (2001 film)|Othello]]'' || [[Iago|Ben Jago]] || Television film\n|-\n|''[[Linda Green]]'' || Tom Sherry / Neil Sherry || Episode: \"Twins\"\n|-\n| rowspan=4|2002 || ''[[The League of Gentlemen]]'' || Dougal Siepp || Episode: \"How the Elephant Got Its Trunk\"\n|-\n| ''Flesh and Blood'' || Joe Broughton || Television film\n|-\n| ''The King and Us'' || Anthony || Television film\n|-\n| ''[[Sunday (2002 film)|Sunday]]'' || General Ford || Television film\n|-\n| 2003 || ''[[The Second Coming (TV serial)|The Second Coming]]'' || Stephen Baxter || 2 episodes\n|-\n| 2005 || ''[[Doctor Who]]'' ||[[Ninth Doctor]]||[[Doctor Who (Series 1)|Series 1]]; 13 episodes\n|-\n| 2005\u20132007 || ''Kings and Pharaohs'' ||Pharaoh Rameses||Lead role\n|-\n| 2006 || ''[[Perfect Parents]]'' || Stuart || Television film\n|-\n| 2007 || ''[[Heroes (U.S. TV series)|Heroes]]'' || [[Claude (Heroes)|Claude]] || 5 episodes\n|-\n| 2008 || ''[[The Sarah Silverman Program]]'' || Dr. Lazer Rage || Episode: \"I Thought My Dad Was Dead, But It Turns O